				<DIV>CLASS: Magician
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP: Moderately important.&nbsp; Meaningless on most raids.&nbsp; Helpful when solo-ing.<BR>Mana:&nbsp; Very Important.&nbsp; Determines ability to cast throughout a fight.&nbsp; Meaningful for long fights.<BR>Endurance:&nbsp; No impact at all<BR>AC: Helpful if you get hit.&nbsp; Mitigates incoming damage and helps you survive a couple rounds.&nbsp; Means more when soloing and assisting your pet.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP Regen: Barely helpful.&nbsp; Numbers are not very high.&nbsp; Helps a little when solo-ing but healing potions made it somewhat unimportant.<BR>Mana Regen: Used to be important.&nbsp; Now with 10000 mana pool the norm.&nbsp; 15 vs 25 mana regen doesn't mean anything.<BR>Endurance Regen:&nbsp; No use whatsoever</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Strength: If you can walk with everything you carry thats all that matters.<BR>Stamina: Tiny HP increase.&nbsp; Basically negligible.<BR>Agility: Moderately important to help avoid incoming melee.<BR>Dexterity: Very important for Critical DD nukes<BR>Charisma: Unimportant<BR>Intelligence: Important for spellcasting and mana pool<BR>Wisdom: Unused by Mages</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Cold Resist: Important for cold nukes.&nbsp; Unused mostly after Velious<BR>Disease Resist: Important for OOW, GoD. Mostly needed for raids<BR>Poison Resist: Important for OOW, GoD. Mostly needed for raids<BR>Magic Resist: Very important for fear, root, snare, mezz, etc.<BR>Fire Resist: Important for fire nukes.&nbsp; Mostly needed for raids</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Attack: Not impotant<BR>Delay: Not impotant<BR>Damage: Not impotant<BR>Range: Not impotant</DIV>
<DIV>Haste: Not impotant</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Combat Effects: Not impotant<BR>Shielding: Important in high end game to increase survivability<BR>Stun Resist: Important to cast new pets if in trouble<BR>Strikethrough: Unused&nbsp;<BR>Spell Shield: Important to avoid nukes<BR>Avoidance:&nbsp; Important in high end game to increase survivability<BR>Accuracy: Unused<BR>DOT Shielding:&nbsp; Important in high end game to increase survivability</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Skill Mods: Not very important<BR>Click Effects: Depending upon effect.&nbsp; Most are resists with minimal benefits<BR>Proc Effects: Other than mana drain not very useful<BR>Worn Effects: depends which one (see all the above)<BR>Focus Effects: Critical.&nbsp; All pet focus are missing (Pet summonging haste is NEEDED beyond level 65!!)<BR></DIV></DIV>
				
