<DIV>Accuracy...yes please</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>And the 1 big thing that is important in this area would be +bs damage.&nbsp; It pains me to have to keep my time bp because I am not yet maxed at 125.&nbsp; It was a great start that you guys added 3 items in demi plane with +bs damage on it thank you very much for that, but I just hope that there will be more options in the future.&nbsp; Having to wear gear that is from pop, god, and anguish because I can't afford to replace them due to the decrease in my dps (which is my main role I might add) is very discouraging.&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
