<div>&nbsp;</div>

<div>HP: Critical.&nbsp; Enchanters get beat on more than any non-tank class.&nbsp; HPs give us a slim chance of surviving it.<br>Mana:
Irrelevant.&nbsp; My gear all has mana on it because gear at this level
does, but I never look at the numbers.&nbsp; I die before I run out of
mana 99% of the time. For that other 1%, there's Gather Mana.<br>Endurance: Obviously Irrelevant.<br>AC: Mostly irrelevant. The current returns on this are so laughable that I can't see giving it any priority.<br>
 </div>

<div>&nbsp;</div>

<div>HP Regen: Irrelevant for all useful intents and purposes.<br>Mana
Regen: Was once moderately important, now is another number I don't
even look at.&nbsp; I routinely catch myself looking at a piece of
gearing and thinking "Oh. That has mana regen on it."&nbsp; The cap is
so easy to reach at this level of progression that it's beside the
point.<br>Endurance Regen:&nbsp; This stat doesn't actually EXIST.<br>
 </div>

<div>&nbsp;</div>

<div>Strength: Irrelevant.<br>Stamina: Good to keep at cap, but so easy at this gear level that it's irrelevant.<br>Agility: Less irrelevant than it used to be, but still not something I'd assign any great priority.<br>Dexterity: Completely worthless.<br>Charisma: Important, and surprisingly hard for an enchanter to keep at cap. <br>Intelligence: Irrelevant. I'm over my cap by something like 150pts.&nbsp; <br>Wisdom: Irrelevant.&nbsp; Not a stat for my class.<br>
 </div>

<div>&nbsp;</div>

<div>Cold Resist: Moderately useful<br>Disease Resist: Moderately useful<br>Poison Resist: Moderately useful<br>Magic Resist: Moderately useful<br>Fire Resist: Moderately useful </div>

<div>&nbsp;<br>
Generally, unless I have on resist that is falling far behind the
others, I look at "total resists" rather than any single resist in
particular.<br>
<br>
</div>

<div>Attack: Irrelevant.<br>
Delay: Irrelevant.<br>Damage: Irrelevant. I don't even hold a weapon these days.<br>Range: No need.<br>
 </div>

<div>Haste: Irrelevant.<br>
 </div>

<div>&nbsp;</div>

<div>Combat Effects: Irrelevant.<br>Shielding: Very small returns here,
but I'm working on it just because I have nothing else other than HP to
improve my survivability.<br>Stun Resist: Critical up to cap, irrelevant once that cap is passed. Not getting stunned is crucial.<br>Strikethrough: Irrelevant.<br>Spell Shield: Moderately relevant. Seems very easy to get, and its utility is diminished by our runes.<br>Avoidance: Critical to cap out.&nbsp; Enchanters geat beat down in melee a lot, and this helps us live.<br>Accuracy: Irrelevant.<br>DOT Shielding: Fairly important.&nbsp; Beats out spell shielding because our rune spells don't help against DoTs.<br>
 </div>

